PrecisAmendments to the LIVESTOCK CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS which are designed to improve the accuracy of HOG CARCASS grading by altering the mathematical equations used to determine the lean yield content of hog carcasses graded with an electronic probe or, in cases where a carcass must be manually graded, by requiring the use of an approved ruler to measure the backfat.
